<p>OK this? This is worlds better than the original. Very much upvoted.</p>
<p>Two notes:</p>
<p>1) Even though we are using metric measurements, I think the general consensus is to use the American spelling &quot;meters&quot; as opposed to &quot;metres&quot;<br />
